org.apache.ignite.lang

Class IgniteUuid

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.lang.IgniteUuid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<IgniteUuid>, Iterable<IgniteUuid>, Binarylizable

    public final class IgniteUuid
extends Object
implements Comparable<IgniteUuid>, Iterable<IgniteUuid>, Cloneable, Externalizable, Binarylizable
    This is a faster performing version of UUID. On basic tests this version is at least 10x time faster for ID creation. It uses extra memory for 8-byte counter additionally to internal UUID.
    See Also:
